dc_title_s: Plan of proposed bulkhead under contract 92 in the Bayhead-Manasquan Canal, Point Pleasant, New Jersey, sheets 1-3
dc_description_s: This plan consists of three sheets of stapled blueprints which depict the location plan, detail plans, sections, and elevations for construction of the Bayhead-Manasquan Canal (now known as the Point Pleasant Canal).|Source map supplied by New Jersey Department of Environmental Protection
